{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"21":{"eng-name":"Funerals (Kitab Al-Jana'iz)","ara-name":"كتاب الجنائز"}},"section_detail":{"21":{"hadithnumber_first":3089,"hadithnumber_last":3241,"arabicnumber_first":3089,"arabicnumber_last":3241}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3172,"arabicnumber":3172,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُسَدَّدٌ، حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ، عَنِ الزُّهْرِيِّ، عَنْ سَالِمٍ، عَنْ أَبِيهِ، عَنْ عَامِرِ بْنِ رَبِيعَةَ، يَبْلُغُ بِهِ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم ‏ \"‏ إِذَا رَأَيْتُمُ الْجَنَازَةَ فَقُومُوا لَهَا حَتَّى تُخَلِّفَكُمْ أَوْ تُوضَعَ ‏\"‏ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1307) Sahih Muslim (958)"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":84},"chapter":{"id":47,"ara-name":"باب الْقِيَامِ لِلْجَنَازَةِ","eng-name":"Standing Up For A Funeral","isFirstHadith":true}}]}